The tribunal can:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>uphold the <abbr title=\"Criminal Injuries Compensation Authority\">CICA</abbr>&rsquo;s decision</li>\n  <li>increase or reduce your award</li>\n  <li>decide you shouldn&rsquo;t get anything</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice help-notice\">\n<p>You have 90 days to appeal to the tribunal from the date of the <abbr title=\"Criminal Injuries Compensation Authority\">CICA</abbr>’s review decision.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>If you miss the deadline, explain why you&rsquo;re late - eg if you&rsquo;re waiting for medical reports.</p>\n\n<h2>Help and advice</h2>\n\n<p>You can represent yourself at the tribunal, but you may want to get help and advice before you appeal.</p>\n\n<p>You can contact:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>a <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://legaladviserfinder.justice.gov.uk/AdviserSearch.do\" title=\"legal adviser\">legal adviser</a></li>\n  <li><a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.victimsupport.org.uk/\" title=\"Victim Support\">Victim Support</a></li>\n  <li>a <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://victimservices.justice.gov.uk/\" title=\"local victim services group\">local victim services group</a></li>\n  <li><a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.citizensadvice.org.uk/\" title=\"Citizens Advice\">Citizens Advice</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n"},{"web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/criminal-injuries-compensation-tribunal/appeal-to-tribunal","slug":"appeal-to-tribunal","order":2,"title":"Appeal to the tribunal","body":"<p>To appeal, fill in the form below, giving reasons why you disagree with the <abbr title=\"Criminal Injuries Compensation Authority\">CICA</abbr>&rsquo;s decision.</p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.justice.gov.uk/downloads/forms/tribunals/cic/NoticeOfAppeal.pdf\" title=\"appeal form (PDF, 64KB)\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘Appeal form’ (PDF, 64KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<p>You must also provide:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>the decision letter from the <abbr title=\"Criminal Injuries Compensation Authority\">CICA